This is where EIDORS keep the files to be compiled with mex:

This this really really difficult because matlab support for mex on older
platforms is worse than non-existant. Here is some advice, 



LINUX:
  Older versions of matlab require a switch like this:
   mex CC=gcc-4.4 CXX=g++-4.4 -largeArrayDims eidors_var_id.cpp
